  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. A screening sensitivity exercise was conducted informally to rank input parameter influence on predicted yield force; titanium alloy elastic modulus and cortical shell thickness were identified as the dominant drivers. This screening informed acceptance-criteria tightening but was not formalized as a structured sensitivity analysis node within the credibility package.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/req/f1717-compression-bending-req",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/claim/cou1-noncannulated-fea-claim",
