      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used under an FDA-validated QMS. Software version controlled in Git; regression suite of 47 benchmark cases executed and passed prior to study. QA plan on file with OSEL quality management system."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
