      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities replicate COU geometry, loading, and material conditions with documented similarity argument.",
      "rationale": "Validation constructs are the same 7.5 mm non-cannulated pedicle screw design as the COU device. Loading replicates ASTM F1717 which is the regulatory standard for this device class. Similarity argument documented in simulation plan section 4.3, confirming that the validation domain encompasses the intended clinical use envelope for static compression-bending."
